### ----------------------------------------------------
### 1. GENERAL / PUBLIC BANK API
### ----------------------------------------------------

### Get Active Banks List (Organizer Selection)
GET {{baseUrl}}/verification/banks
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}


### ----------------------------------------------------
### 2. ADMIN BANK CRUD MANAGEMENT APIs
### ----------------------------------------------------

### Step 2.1: Admin Adds a New Mongolian Bank
POST {{baseUrl}}/verification/banks/admin
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "bankName": "Arig Bank"
}

### Step 2.2: Admin Updates a Bank Name or Status
# Replace bankId below with actual mongo ObjectId of a bank
PUT {{baseUrl}}/verification/banks/admin/665efb5f1cd98a221f7c320d
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "bankName": "Arig Bank Mongolia",
  "isActive": true
}

### Step 2.3: Admin Deletes a Bank
# Replace bankId below with actual mongo ObjectId of a bank
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/verification/banks/admin/665efb5f1cd98a221f7c320d
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
